(7, 'en', 'Trefoil Hoodie', '', '', '<p>The adidas Originals Trefoil Hoodie has been a streetwear essential for  decades, with its characteristic big hood, kangaroo pocket and large  Trefoil. Now it\'s your turn to join the Trefoil men\'s hoodie crew and  carry the legend forward.</p>', '', '', '', '', '', '<p class=\"product-promo-text\"><span class=\"product-promo-header\">FREE US shipping over $100!</span><span class=\"product-promo-body\">Orders within next 2 days will be shipped on Monday</span></p>'),
